<h4 id="лІ„нӮ·-лӮҳм—ҙ">лІ„нӮ· лӮҳм—ҙ</h4>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">boto3</span>
